<TITLE>
Mateguas, the Ghost Rabbit (Matiguas, Matgwas) 
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Mateguas (Matiguas),
the Abenaki lord of the dead.">
