<a name="tribes">Mateguas Stories</a>
</u></H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jiibayaabooz
">Jiibayaabooz/Mateguas</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Wikipedia article about incarnations of the Spirit Rabbit in Chippewa and Abenaki mythology.
<BR>

